sectionText: Prerequisites will be enforced. This section will open to all students in the College of Business and to Food Science & Human Nutrition majors on Monday, November 14, 2016 and to Technical Systems Management and ISE students on November 28, 2016 at approximately 9:00 a.m. There are currently 10 reserved seats for College of Business international exchange students; any unused seats will be released to students meeting the restrictions on Friday, January 20, 2017 at approximately 9:00 a.m.
